_sText:
Haven't done any maps in a long time thought this would be a good one to start with. 

There are 2 spawn places for each team. One is on the top of bridge the othere is on the catwalk just under the bridge. I did this so the hole bridge is used. By the pitcures you can't see there is a door in the tunnel to get from the top to catwalk faster. Othere then jumping down, you can do this without killing yourself from both sides.

 I hope you like it . 

Any and all comments welcomed. :) 


*EDIT*

This map is now an Aim map. aim_BlownBridge
